Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing, Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so good at this.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be enjoying \Nthe praise all the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really good too, Tsumugu{-kun}.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you learn how to cook?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always been just \NGramps and me, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! That's so responsible of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We don't need that \Nmuch Chinese cabbage.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.69,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't we all go around to \Nthe other groups and try their food too?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.71,0:03:26.35,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme try some of yours.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? The carrot's huge.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.04,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,please try ours too!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.54,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Try yours?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As if sea people could make \Nanything even remotely edible.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells like fish, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.64,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But there isn't any fish in it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.14,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really think it's fine—
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.68,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I don't want any!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu{-kun}...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just an accident.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.43,0:04:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.83,0:04:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat your lunch?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We just ate.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go work \Non the Wooden Maiden.{—}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you think we should \Ntry to get along with them a bit more?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,20,,You mean{,} with the guys that waste food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.00,Oshit Oshit; Fishy Business,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\c&H681706&\b1\fscx149\fscy134\org(606,735)\frx358\fry338\fax-0.08\pos(601,629)}W{*\fax-0.072}o{*\fax-0.064}o{*\fax-0.056}d {\fax-0.04}S{*\fax-0.026}h{*\fax-0.012}o{*\fax0.002}p {\fax0.03\c&H751B08&}Room
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.03,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would do something like this?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was them.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Half-arm suplex!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.77,0:05:34.86,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on, q-quit it!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chest!{This comes back again at the end of the episode. ~_~}{its some japanese martial arts battlecry, it was parodied in katanagatari too. i dont know the particulars tbh}{}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.82,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was indeed reprehensible that the Wooden Maiden was broken{, but still..}.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We had nothing to do with that!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit lying!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.14,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else would've done it?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, come on. Please stop.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.33,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.93,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you're too worked up for this to get resolved today.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We should come back to it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, you can go home for today.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one you're sending home?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I'm \Nthe only one at fault here?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.88,0:06:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}excuse{\i0} me!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have fourth period...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home, \Nso I'm going home!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...{}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.57,0:06:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka's so stubborn \Nwhen she gets like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this isn't coming off at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka's so cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be a scaredy cat, \Nbut she has a strong will,{;}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a {nice, }really slender body,{;}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and big, round eyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's always trying so hard.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're big.{Like, not thin/slender/skinny, right?}{haha uhhh hes saying manaka appears tiny and cute to chisaki because chisaki isnt as slender and taller}{you can see this 0639}{}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too blunt, Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are guys who prefer \Ntaller girls too, you know.{who prefer taller girls}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.96,0:06:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And apparently, middle-aged men prefer girls who aren't so skinny.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.72,0:06:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've left that part out.{ugh. pretty sure this is more like 'stop trying to stick up for me'}{I was thinking it was more like, "Thanks. Now I feel so much better."}{}{saying that doesnt help}{lit. saying that doesnt back me up}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just be honest \Nwith yourself and be happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably should learn to \Nbe more honest, like Manaka.
