Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sayu wuz heer"?{the spelling is horribly wrong here, might want to reflect that}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.34,0:07:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.36,0:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0, 21,She's one of those mysterious grade schoolers who have a grudge against Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Grade schoolers?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty straightforward \Nadmission of guilt.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the guys \Nfrom our class after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.83,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.07,0:07:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep this a secret.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's pretend we didn't see it, Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.98,0:07:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if everyone else \Nfinds out about this,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari will wind up \Nlooking like the bad guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.37,0:07:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see him get hurt \Nor blamed any more!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.96,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But bad guy or not, the truth is \Nthat it was a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.07,0:07:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to lie.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll only isolate you even more.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, though!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.25,0:08:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the people who said our food smelled like fish!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not bad people \Nonce you get to know them.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The same people who spilled our sushi bowl on purpose?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were a \Ngood person, Tsumugu{-kun},
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.96,0:08:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess you're just like any other person from the surface{ after all}.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.52,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki loses her head when it comes to Hikari or Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.79,0:08:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I love both the sea and \Nthe people of Shishio.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.85,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}That's why I don't want everyone to misunderstand \NHikari just because he misunderstands all of them.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you repeat that?{lol...}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.89,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want everyone to misunderstand Hikari \Njust because he misunderstands all of them.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
