Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.25,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miuna{-chan} was so cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She acted like my baby sister.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.66,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them, and Itaru{-san} too... They were the perfect family{ for me}.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They were always smiling.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,at Miori{-san}'s funeral...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna{-chan} was bawling.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I had never seen her cry like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.72,0:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It somehow reminded me of \NHikari when he was younger.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And right then...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.85,0:14:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought to myself
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.72,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that I wanted to stay beside them.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could maybe \Nfill the hole {that }Miori{-san} left behind.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you're \Nsugarcoating it a bit?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.78,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just forbidden love.{wow literal}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.40,0:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Miori was gone, and you \Nwanted to take her place.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.83,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's harsh, {replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama}.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I could put a curse on you, if you want.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.58,0:14:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A curse?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A curse to make you forget \Nthe man you fell for.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of this on my own.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still such a child.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.70,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only so much \Nyou can do on your own.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.54,0:14:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Lord Sea God.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.04,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't hand over the people \Nof the sea to the surface just yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wooden Maiden.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.30,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.75,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who ruined it!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.71,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.61,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you get mad at her, Hii{-kun}?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not like \NI don't know how she feels.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When my mom died, if some other \Nwoman had tried to come into my house,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably wouldn't have liked it either.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you crying?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} told me
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.54,0:16:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that I always rely on you and \NChii{-chan} and Kaname to protect me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} said that?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think it's true.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.70,0:16:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Uroko{Uroko-sama} says something useful every now and then.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}, you're kind.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really kind.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You put others before \Nyourself and protect them...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.59,0:16:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, let's go and \Napologize to everyone together!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I bet they're gonna have a lot to say in return.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they'll have \Na lot to say to me, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.92,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.59,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect you from now on, Hii{-kun}.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} protect you.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.51,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.95,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was supposed to be \Nthe one to protect {\i0}her{\i1}.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.77,0:17:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But instead, she protected me, \Njust like Ena does.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.99,0:17:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you two have a sec?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} want?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.22,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.90,0:17:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.96,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm sorry I thought it was you who destroyed the Wooden Maiden.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's enough, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.90,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dude, he's totally on his knees.{bg}{During Chisaki's line.}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.02,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I never saw anyone do that.{bg}{right after the last one}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.02,0:17:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun} feels really bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive him.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive them already.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.21,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ones responsible for their \Nsushi bowl spilling, so let's just call it even.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true you guys \Nspilled our sushi bowl!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.96,0:18:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I blamed you for it, \Nand then I tackled you!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.30,0:18:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So forgive me,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.74,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and then...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,come at me!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chest!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already. This is annoying.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you {\i1}ever{\i0} go to school?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.59,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're the one to blame for \NHikari{'s} getting down on his knees like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.21,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari is my best friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.05,0:19:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And as his best friend, I can't let that go.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.78,0:19:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm... I'm Miuna's friend too!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.14,0:19:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my very bestest friend!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in second grade,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone used to pick on me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.59,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miuna never did.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, people started \Npicking on her instead.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.72,0:20:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was kind of relieved,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.18,0:20:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,since it wasn't me who was getting picked on anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miuna...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much they ignored her,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,she was totally fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.82,0:20:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be okay with this?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.99,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you okay with getting bullied and with people not liking you?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.81,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're people I don't care about, \Nand they have nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't care what they think of me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When she said that,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.52,0:20:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped caring what people \Nthought about me, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even care if people hated me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.45,0:20:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All that mattered was that \NMiuna and I were friends!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you apologize to Hikari?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.95,0:21:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you understand how dear \Nsomeone can be to you, you can, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.57,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.03,0:21:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm... really sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, please forgive her.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.39,0:21:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.54,0:21:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.07,0:21:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did she...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.31,0:21:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:30.36,0:21:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.73,0:21:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, how lame.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.68,0:21:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got snot coming out your nose.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.28,0:21:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up, you octopus—
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Lord Octopus{Octopus-sama}!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.11,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Adding a "Lord"{Tacking on a "-sama"} doesn't just make everything better!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.69,0:21:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:52.03,0:21:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to defend Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.65,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:07.45,ED-english,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,450)\blur2.5}Detritus floats in the warm water
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:07.45,ED-romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,450)\blur2.5}atatakai mizu ni oyogu detritus
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:10.81,ED-english,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2.5}I take it, and spend a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:10.81,ED-romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2.5}nagai jikan wo kakete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:19.96,ED-english,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,450)\blur2.5}spinning it into a cocoon for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:19.96,ED-romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,450)\blur2.5}ito wo tsumuginagara mayu ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:34.11,ED-english,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2.5}How long did we have
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:34.11,ED-romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2.5}ittai dore kurai mabuta wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:37.43,ED-english,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2.5}our eyes closed?
